 (56,8,'_about_us_intro_step2_desc','You can see a doctor whenever you want, wherever you are, on your PC, laptop, tablet or mobile phone. And if your consultation results in a prescription, we can email, fax or post it to you or your chosen pharmacy or you can get your medication delivered to your door.'),
