 (71,8,'_about_us_our_mission_intro_text','<p>Technology may be at the core of how we work, but we’re a healthcare company at heart. And we want to make healthcare better.</p>'),
 (72,8,'_about_us_our_mission_content','<p>To do this, we’re putting your healthcare in your hands, giving you a place to manage your medical records and see a doctor whenever you need to. We’re not simply a video portal between you and a doctor. We’re a complete clinical solution that combines the best attributes of the hands-on medical profession with the convenience of modern technology. </p>\r\n<p>Through recruiting hundreds of the UK’s most trusted GPs, consultants, therapists and psychologists, we’ve become one of the UK’s leading online healthcare service providers. We’ve increased access to high quality, convenient and affordable healthcare. And by always putting patients first and working non-stop to exceed their expectations, we’re only going to get better.</p>'),
