 (123,19,'_how_it_works_intro_intro_text','<p>Doctors use two main skills to diagnose most common medical conditions: looking and listening. By using the latest video technology, VideoDoc lets you have a face to face appointment with a doctor or other healthcare provider on your PC, laptop or mobile device within minutes. <strong>Here\'s how it works.</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"> </p>'),
 (124,19,'_how_it_works_steps_step1_title','1. Check in'),
 (125,19,'_how_it_works_steps_step1_desc','<ul class=\"bullets\">\r\n<li>Tell us a little about yourself: name, date of birth, reason for visit, current medications</li>\r\n<li>It\'s helpful if you have to hand details of your preferred pharmacy</li>\r\n<li>You can upload photos, scans or documents if you feel they’ll help the doctor reach their diagnosis</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-24 size-full\" src=\"http://videodoc.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/step1.png\" alt=\"step1\" width=\"112\" height=\"121\" /></p>'),
 (126,19,'_how_it_works_steps_step2_title','2. See a GP'),
 (127,19,'_how_it_works_steps_step2_desc','<ul class=\"bullets\">\r\n<li class=\"standard-text\">You can choose a GP by clicking <a href=\"https://www.evideodoc.co.uk\" class=\"green-text\">See a Doctor now</a>, or you can make an appointment with a GP or other healthcare provider by selecting <a href=\"\">Get an appointment now</a></li>\r\n<li>We\'ll send you an alert or text message when your doctor is ready</li>\r\n<li>You\'ll then have a face to face appointment on your PC, laptop, tablet or mobile phone. The average waiting time for a non-scheduled appointment is only a few minutes.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-31 size-full\" src=\"http://videodoc.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/step2.png\" alt=\"step2\" width=\"112\" height=\"121\" /></p>'),
 (128,19,'_how_it_works_steps_step3_title','3. Receive diagnosis, get your prescription, referral letter or sick note'),
 (129,19,'_how_it_works_steps_step3_desc','<ul class=\"bullets\">\r\n<li>After your consultation we\'ll send you an email letting you know your written diagnosis is available to view online</li>\r\n<li>These details are automatically saved to your VideoDoc medical record which you can view whenever you like </li>\r\n<li>Our doctors can email or fax your prescription to you or your chosen pharmacy. Or you can order your prescription and get it delivered to your door</li>\r\n<li>If you need a referral letter or fit note this can be faxed, emailed or posted to you </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-32 size-full\" src=\"http://videodoc.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/step3.png\" alt=\"step3\" width=\"112\" height=\"121\" /></p>'),
