 (156,85,'_doctors_intro_content','<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">VideoDoc has been developed with the guidance of clinicians, global software developers and industry professionals. By using the latest internet and video technology, it lets doctors have online, face to face appointments with patients within minutes.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
