 (159,85,'_doctors_benefits_intro','<h3>If you\'re a GP or other healthcare provider VideoDoc lets you treat and write prescriptions for patients who may have physical, mental and emotional issues.<br /><br />It\'s your chance to:<br /><br /></h3>'),
 (160,85,'_doctors_benefits_points','<ul class=\"cross\">\r\n<li>Work from your practice, at home, or anywhere you want</li>\r\n<li>Increase revenue</li>\r\n<li>Be in control of when you work with our online scheduling</li>\r\n<li>Expand your patient outreach</li>\r\n<li>Empower your patients with online scheduling and medical services</li>\r\n<li>Reduce limitations of physical boundaries and office hours</li>\r\n<li>Work in a paperless environment</li>\r\n<li>Minimise costs</li>\r\n<li>Enhance efficiency and patient care</li>\r\n<li>Offer access to further, convenient medical care</li>\r\n<li>Increase patient satisfaction</li>\r\n</ul>'),
 (161,85,'_doctors_benefits_box','<p>Led by Consultant Cardiologist Dr. Robert Kelly, our medical team comprises some of Ireland’s leading healthcare professionals. We are always looking to more to join the team.</p>'),
