 (640,240,'_pharmacies_intro_content','<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Join our network of pharmacies offering walk-in online primary care clinics</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>We\'re helping people see a doctor whenever they want, wherever they are, on their PCs, laptops, tablets and mobile phones. However, not everyone has the technology needed to access our service. This is where you can help.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>With VideoDoc, you can offer people in your local area an online consultation with a doctor for just £22. All they need to do is pop in, log on and tell us what\'s wrong. And if their appointment leads to a prescription, they can pick it up from you there and then.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>');
